 ulykker. Men omveltningene er vel s\u00e5 store for personer som akkurat har f\u00e5tt vite at de har kreft. Mennesket som ble utsatt for ulykken, vet at hun har overlevd. Det er ikke kreftpasienten sikker p\u00e5 enn\u00e5."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "aab53da2fe3bfc5c02260575ee521671b9507d0b13f3e8ada4e0d437fcc78513"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-04-28T12:11:52.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Sykepleier Marit Berg Kahn nektet \u00e5 innse at alt h\u00e5p var ute. Hun opps\u00f8kte legen Thomas Johansson som ga henne misteltein mot kreften."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1066733.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/ver2%20kvakksalver3"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/b9d1eee6d3ef28c2274b9b24f0869349849bd11f.jpg?598a4bc0"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "Behandler kreftsyke med misteltein-ekstrakt -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "b9d1eee6d3ef28c2274b9b24f0869349849bd11f"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "health-and-fitness"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["misteltein", "behandler", "alternativ", "lege", "kreft", "alternativ behandler"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["st. olavs", "berg kahn", "kvakksalverloven", "berg kahn og johansson"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "tyskland"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["thomas johansson", "marit berg kahn"]}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://